Package au.edu.anu.twcore

Class TextTranslations

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.edu.anu.twcore.TextTranslations
  • public class TextTranslations
extends java.lang.Object
    Natural language translations for any message in this project (twcore).

    Currently, only French and English are supported. These messages are all related to the query system through this need not be the case. By convention, query translation methods are named after the relevant query. Query messages have two forms:

  • am: the Action message - action to take to address the problem e.g Do this...
  • cm: the Compliance message - the condition that caused the message e.g Expected this but found this...

    • Ensure default response is English otherwise unhandled languages will not produce a message.

Author:
Ian Davies - 14 Mar. 2021
